Build & Run
  docker-compose build
  docker-compose up -d
  docker ps
--------------------------------
Access the Lab
  docker exec -it linuxlab /bin/bash 
                OR 
  docker exec -it <container_name> /bin/bash (Check Container Name)

  exit  ( To Exit shell)
------------------------------
System Information
  hostname ( To Check hostname)
  ip addr show (Check IP address)
  cat /etc/os-release ( Check OS version)

File & Directory Management
  ls -l /root (List files)
  cat /root/myconfig.txt (View mounted config)
  vim /root/myconfig.txt (Edit file with vim)

Networking
  ping 172.28.0.10 (Ping test)
  ip route (Check routes)
  ifconfig (Legacy ifconfig)

Process & System Monitoring
  ps aux (List processes)
  top (Check CPU/memory usage)
  df -h (Disk usage)

Exiting & Managing Container

  exit (Exit shell)


